            Bio
            Huang Anni studies neural networks and their applications
            at Singapore Management University. Her research focuses on
            time-series analysis in semi-conductor domain and
            reinforcement learning in gaming industry. She frequently
            collaborates with researchers who study machine learning,
            and cognitive science.
